          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1610983146835-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1610983146835-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1610983146835-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> sriracha</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a small bowl – this is your<strong> buffalo sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1610983651709-x200.jpg",
