    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
